text: Sulzfeld is a municipality in Rhön-Grabfeld in Bavaria in Germany. It has the following villages: Kleinbardorf, Leinach, Sulzfeld, Sulzfelder Forst. The large regional Jewish cemetery, Jewish Cemetery (Kleinbardorf) is also in Sulzfeld. ==References== Category:Rhön-Grabfeld
title: Sulzfeld, Rhön-Grabfeld
